from employees and leaders

00:04:09.101 --> 00:04:11.126
about the impact of this kind of behavior,

00:04:11.150 --> 00:04:12.499
the more he became convinced

00:04:12.523 --> 00:04:14.642
that it must have an actual,
measurable cost.

